These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Transport: train, skateboard, motorbike, taxi
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Transport:skateboard##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Transport:train##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Transport:skateboard is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1
6. Transport:skateboard is somewhere to the left of Transport:train##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Transport      | motorbike  | skateboard | taxi        | train |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Birthday: february, november, june, may
Sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is somewhere between Sport:skateboarding and Birthday:june##7
2. Birthday:may is somewhere to the left of Birthday:february##5
3. Birthday:may is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
4. Birthday:november is on the left of Birthday:may##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Birthday     | june | november       | may         | february     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

